This directory contains three separate projects used to supporting SQL Anywhere.They are:

./sqlanywhere
   - This is the main driver that allows Ruby to to connect to DBCAPI
   - It is built and distributed as a gem called 'sqlanywhere'

./dbd-sqlanywhere
   - This is a pure-Ruby driver for the Ruby DBI interface
   - This driver relies on the 'sqlanywhere' gem already being installed

./activerecord-sqlanywhere-adapter
   - This is a pure-Ruby ActiveRecord drive used by Ruby on Rails
   - This driver is itself a pure-Ruby gem
   - This driver relies on the 'sqlanywhere' gem already being installed
